QuestData.Title: Tangleheart
QuestData.Description:
Hey there, peach. We've got the lumber mill good and ready, but we gotta find a way of choppin' wood fast out here.
The Laughing Skull talked about Tangleheart, where the botani grow things quick as a quark.
I'm headin' there now.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Penny Clobberbottom outside Tangleheart.
QuestData.RewardText: Hey! Looky what I found here.
